# Project Rules

## Stack
- Next.js 15 with App Router
- TypeScript strict mode
- Tailwind CSS v4
- Supabase for database

## Code Style
- Functional components only
- Named exports for components
- Use `cn()` helper for conditional classes
- Prefer server components

## File Organization
- Components in `src/components/`
- Shared UI in `src/components/ui/`
- Utilities in `src/lib/`
- Types in `src/types/`

## Supabase
- Browser client: `import { createClient } from '@/lib/supabase/client'`
- Server client: `import { createClient } from '@/lib/supabase/server'`
- Always use typed queries

## Git
- Never push to main
- Feature branches → staging → main
- Run `pnpm type-check` before commits
